Change the subscription status or contract of a product in the basket.
Only available when SUBSCRIBE_AND_SAVE feature is enabled.

If a null basketId is provided, this will fall back to the logged in customer's saved basket, or a new basket.
This may return a different basket ID than provided, if the basket moved, merged, or didn't exist.

The toSubscription input field is used to specify the direction in which to switch:
- true: Switch from normal product to subscription, or change existing subscription contract
- false: Switch from subscription product to normal product

When switching to a normal product, contractId can be omitted.

@param basketId Optional basket ID to modify
@param sku Product SKU to modify
@param contractId Optional ID of the new subscription contract
@param settings Session settings
@param fulfilmentInput Click and collect details if applicable
@param toSubscription Whether to switch to subscription (true) or normal product (false)

